title: Thai Snack
typeOfFood: Ovo, Thai, Fast food, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Thai street-food style dining with a selection of noodle dishes and curries that could be requested without egg, papaya salad requested without fish sauce, plus has several vegetable-based dishes. Lively atmosphere, frequented by expats. Attached to a male-male massage parlor. Menu: www.gulfdine.com/Thai-Snack-House_Al-Nasr-St
